
                         (Extract)                        (Calculation)
Database(SQL server..)  ----------->   Rpt tool(Tableau)  -------------->  Report
                                        .tde                                chart..
                                        power pivot                        pivot table
                              



Tableau
  Live
  Extract
  
PowerBI
  Extract(PowerPivot) by default
  have option to refresh connection to database
  have option to refresh connection data model
  
SSRS 
  no extract
  Live connect to source by default(Often have dedicated source server to host source data)
  Delivery
    cache: cache report with default parameter
    snapshot
  components 
    Report server(has a url, processing core)
    Report server database(stores metadata, compiled reports..)
    Data source
    Report manager(web portal)


Trade-off
Report Performance vs. Latency
  Max Latency: Frequency of Extract from source
